      "comment": "Manners let STAR OF PATRICK (2) down when he started favourite last start but he had done well to come from wider draws than this for fourth in first two starts back from a spell. Race fit and is likely to get the favours from this nice draw. Winning chance if he gets it right. BITTA IRISH LUCK (6) started from a 20m handicap and raced three wide without cover when resuming with a respectable second at this circuit and distance. Fitter so can progress. PERSEVERANSE (1) led from a couple of spots wider than this and then stuck on for third here last time. That was his sixth top-three result from his last seven stars including a win at this circuit and distance two back. Has claims. CYCLONE S ADAMS NZ (7) is next best",
